{"tid":1680962,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"老實講，每一次去添馬公園集會都有個好痴線嘅現象","createTime":"2019-10-29T06:33:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-29T07:04:29.000Z","uid":34676,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"56e80106f01f40f6110661b921352dd77ae1d0ff","tid":1680962,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:33:31.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">就係海富下面間M 記都勁撚多黑衫人幫襯啊屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n平時行街經過M 記見到多人幫襯<br />\n我都可能安慰自己入面可能全部藍屍<br />\n但有咩理由之前添馬搞集會<br />\n一邊好激昂咁嗌黑警死全家<br />\n一邊就喺海富下面間m 記食人血漢堡？"},{"pid":"d4f539c2883731654eec5e02ba8db30aac57bf75","tid":1680962,"uid":47605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-29T06:34:16.000Z","msg":"我們早前在Telegram成立了手足匿名搵工平台，助手足自行尋找明白其情況的本地良心僱主，幫助他們在漫長保釋（可能講緊一、兩年時間的排期）或長期夢境中，有工開有野做有糧出，同時又可以滿足保釋條件。<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1680524\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1680524</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/findagoodboss\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Ffindagoodboss&d=SKXI%2FGePWbtdtN3kaacFP7e6YIpo%2BX2FdnjHEpUIxFw%3D&h=1e24fb4e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/findagoodboss</a><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"411b09c0972fb44423932b9b49fbddbe275cd156","tid":1680962,"uid":34676,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTim